This is Xander Hudson's <mailto:jar@synoptic.org> excellent "Jar of Fireflies" project, with some code modifications and a couple of board designs in EAGLE.

The main code modification is the addition of darkness detection (using a photoresistor).

Original project: <http://www.instructables.com/id/Jar-of-Fireflies/>

